reviewText: It was what I expected, transfer from VHS is not very quality, but it is an old tape.

Howdy;

Not exactly what I thought it would be, but still interesting on a boring afternoon when you can't go outside 'cause of smoke from the "Rim Wildfire" just over the hill.

The women were okay, but the filmwork wasn't all that great.

I'm still lookin' for the "Not So Little Mermaid".  Anyone see her?

L8R daze...
